</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7A0D59344F75FFFCFF12F95DFEFDF8FF" blockId="2.[151,1436,1709,1795]" pageId="2" pageNumber="377">
Thomas &amp; Orth, in 
<bibRefCitation id="1E2324C54F75FFFCFEDBF95DFD80F93A" author="Thomas, A. &amp; Horeau, V. &amp; Dominique, Y." box="[350,590,1709,1734]" pageId="2" pageNumber="377" pagination="49 - 57" refId="ref7218" refString="Thomas, A., Orth, K., Horeau, V. &amp; Dominique, Y. (2000) Les Ephemeres de la Guyane Francaise. 3. Bessierus doloris n. gen., n. sp. (Ephemeroptera: Leptophlebiidae). Ephemera, 2, 49 - 57." type="journal article" year="2000">
Thomas 
<emphasis id="48C685264F75FFFCFE33F95FFE2CF93A" box="[438,482,1710,1734]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="377">et al</emphasis>
., 2000: 49
</bibRefCitation>
(nymph). (Type-species: 
<taxonomicName id="BDB222B74F75FFFCFCD7F95FFB65F93A" authority="Thomas &amp; Orth" authorityName="Thomas &amp; Orth" box="[850,1195,1709,1734]" class="Insecta" family="Leptophlebiidae" genus="Bessierus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="377" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="doloris">
